text: Cristina Ebner (born 3 September 1938) is an Italian alpine skier. She competed in the women's slalom at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Italy Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
